item.description:
Hey Incubators!!

We'll bring the incubator back to my backyard this week so bring your improv moves on over, lol.

As usual bring smiles, friends, and funny faces as we work our brains and our bodies to make things up on the spot in some exciting improvised games!

Remember no experience required! So come one and come all, especially those who have yet to come out.

Once you get here just come straight around the to backyard!

Also, if any needs a place, i'm looking for a roommate, so you can check that out of you are interested as well.

Cheers!

Jason

p.s. sorry for the uber late notice, twas my birthday earlier this week, i accept people just coming out to the incubator as belated presents!!
item.name: Incubator Up! 3D
